Welcome to MkDocs
¶


For full documentation visit 
mkdocs.org
.


Commands
¶




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.

docs.text:
Descobrir tabelas do GATEC
¶


Se logado com usuário 
gatec_saf


1
SELECT
 
*
 
FROM
 
USER_TABLES
 
WHERE
 
TABLE_NAME
 
LIKE
 
'%PEDIDO%'
 






Se logado com usuário 
queryti


1
SELECT
 
*
 
FROM
 
ALL_TABLES
 
WHERE
 
TABLE_NAME
 
LIKE
 
'%PEDIDO%'
 
AND
 
OWNER
 
=
 
'GATEC_SAF'
;
docs.title: Oracle
